tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE network_performance_data (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  cell_id INT,
  signal_strength INT,
  latency INT
);

CREATE TABLE 5g_network_performance_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    network_type VARCHAR(50),
    download_speed FLOAT,
    upload_speed FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE 5g_optimization_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    cell_id INT,
    optimization_strategy VARCHAR(100),
    performance_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE network_performance_data (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    cell_id INT NOT NULL,
    signal_strength INT,
    latency INT
)

CREATE TABLE cell_towers (
    tower_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    bandwidth INT,
    technology VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE network_optimization (
    optimization_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    details TEXT,
    recommendation TEXT,
    impact VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Network_Performance_Data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  server_id INT,
  network_speed FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Server_Information (
  server_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  provider VARCHAR(255),
  status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE User_Data (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(255),
  phone_number VARCHAR(15)
)

CREATE TABLE Optimization_Logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  action VARCHAR(100),
  description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE network_performance_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  latency_ms FLOAT,
  download_speed_mb FLOAT,
  upload_speed_mb FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE devices (
  device_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model VARCHAR(50),
  os_version VARCHAR(20),
  manufacturer VARCHAR(50),
  network_type VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE network_coverage (
  area_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  coverage_type VARCHAR(20),
  signal_strength FLOAT,
  data_rate_mb FLOAT,
  latency_threshold_ms FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE subscriptions (
  subscription_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  plan_name VARCHAR(50),
  data_limit_gb FLOAT,
  price DECIMAL(10,2),
  start_date DATE,
  expiry_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE users (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(50),
  phone_number VARCHAR(15),
  registration_date DATE
)
